===Noun===
'''progenitor'''
# any of a person's [[direct]] [[ancestor]]s
# a predecessor of something, e.g. "[[wikipedia:ARPANET|ARPANET]] was the ''progenitor'' of the [[Internet]]."
# someone who [[originate]]s or [[found]]s something

